data.description: **BEAUTIFULLY UPDATED, TERRIFIC LOCATION** Prepare to be impressed with this well-maintained and aesthetically updated home conveniently located between Riverview and Tampa with easy access to I-75 and the Crosstown Expressway. The well-crafted home enjoys abundant natural light and a layout designed for easy living and entertaining. When you first walk in, you will notice the stunning and durable WATERPROOF LUXURY PLANK FLOORING that extends throughout the living area. Chef's Kitchen features gorgeous espresso cabinets, tons of counter space, a large prep island and STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES. The living room with its vaulted ceilings this a true centerpiece for gatherings, and sliding glass doors lead out to a covered patio for year-round enjoyment. A luxurious master bedroom with an ensuite bathroom with soaking tub and plenty of closet space provide a quiet retreat. This property also features three other dreamy bedrooms, 2022 HVAC, all fresh paint and flooring, fenced yard, and inside utility. With schools, shops, dining & leisure facilities within easy reach, this is the ideal place to call home. Be prepared for this to be love at first sight! Everything's been done for you, so all you have to do is schedule your showing today before this one is gone!
